Package: xmimsim
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libxmimsim0 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: XMI-MSIM is a software package to simulate ED-XRF spectrometers -- executables
 XMI-MSIM is a software package to simulate the spectral response of energy 
 dispersive X-ray fluorescence  spectrometers using Monte Carlo simulations.
 .
 This package contains the executables necessary to run the package.

Package: libxmimsim0
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libfgsl0, libxslt1.1, libgtkextra3, libhdf5-serial-dev, desktop-file-utils, libxrlf03-3 (>= 2.15.0)
Description: XMI-MSIM is a software package to simulate ED-XRF spectrometers -- core library
 XMI-MSIM is a software package to simulate the spectral response of energy 
 dispersive X-ray fluorescence  spectrometers using Monte Carlo simulations.
 .
 This package contains the shared library and the dataset. 


