Architecture: any
Section: libdevel
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libxmimsim0 (= ${binary:Version}), libfgsl0-dev, libxslt1-dev, libgtkextra3-dev (>= 3.0.1), libhdf5-serial-dev, libgtk2.0-bin, libxrl3-dev (>= 2.15.0)
Description: XMI-MSIM is a software package to simulate ED-XRF spectrometers -- SDK
 XMI-MSIM is a software package to simulate the spectral response of energy 
 dispersive X-ray fluorescence  spectrometers using Monte Carlo simulations.
 .
 This package contains the development components of XMI-MSIM. 



